reviewText: My sister bought me this movie for my birthday and since I'm a huge leif garrett fan,I thought i'd enjoy it.sadly it turned out to be a movie I would not watch again and do not recommend! This movie is for sure rated R,has too much violence,graphic talk,prison situations,etc.the only thing that I like in the movie was the relationship between leif and his friend in the movie,for the most part,and of course leif's acting.
This movie was horrible,one of the worst ones.it was good to see leif but besides that it was terrible.way to much swearing and graphic talk.
